[{"url_token": "pomah016", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "673064717", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "673064717", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "在超市买了一瓶，拿回去喝了一杯半，醉倒不省人事…[捂脸]", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "PomaH016", "author_id": "871d4a6b9cf9d259b23e3f13c9d75853", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": []}, {"url_token": "jun-zi-mo-los", "headline": "不若疏狂", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "314773297", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "314773297", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "<p>做的时候直接加糖是不行的，要加糖浆再静置7天</p>", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "君子墨", "author_id": "2a938820e6cd9673c6ec1a4904e18012", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": [{"url_token": "jiuyanshe", "headline": "专栏“酒研社”作者|公众号 jiuyanshe|解读每一杯酒背后的故事", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "314841017", "reply_comment_id": "314773297", "reply_root_comment_id": "314773297", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "<p>我们的制作图中有哦，加糖后静置7~10天~~突然收到评论，吓得社长赶紧去翻翻图~有写呢~</p>", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "醉酒的社长", "author_id": "ae69934d7cbd67f46b24b68289ddecba", "author_is_anonymous": false}]}, {"url_token": "can-deng-gu-ying-yue-xia-zhu", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "314752438", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "314752438", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "有一个叫“生命之水”的酒行不行😅", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "哎嘿", "author_id": "46843605352e6b5c627fe261d668c661", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": [{"url_token": "jiuyanshe", "headline": "专栏“酒研社”作者|公众号 jiuyanshe|解读每一杯酒背后的故事", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "314754640", "reply_comment_id": "314752438", "reply_root_comment_id": "314752438", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "<p>据我这边了解，如果你说的是“生命之水”波兰伏特加，是可以的，但是这个度数略高啊，还请三思……如果你指的是威士忌的话，理论上来讲，其实只要是烈酒就可以，但是威士忌的风味太过复杂，可能会影响柠檬酒的味道，毕竟柠檬酒还是以酸酸甜甜的口感为主。</p>", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "醉酒的社长", "author_id": "ae69934d7cbd67f46b24b68289ddecba", "author_is_anonymous": false}]}, {"url_token": "li-lun-83-79", "headline": "设计", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "314704468", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "314704468", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "第一张图不是装酒的，是调料瓶，胡椒，盐什么的", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "苍凉的白菜", "author_id": "c163201736226febf13b87163ba535e5", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": [{"url_token": "jiuyanshe", "headline": "专栏“酒研社”作者|公众号 jiuyanshe|解读每一杯酒背后的故事", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "314711459", "reply_comment_id": "314704468", "reply_root_comment_id": "314704468", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "<p>0.0   OMG……谢谢指出~我去找我朋友谈谈人生什么的……</p>", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "醉酒的社长", "author_id": "ae69934d7cbd67f46b24b68289ddecba", "author_is_anonymous": false}]}, {"url_token": "zhi-ma-nian-gao", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "314592232", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "314592232", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "本人英语渣，去意大利的时候，看不懂酒单，当时想着柠檬味的总不会太难喝，点了这个。。。因为不会喝酒，当时就被这么冲的酒味震惊到了。", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "芝麻年糕", "author_id": "b7c99f4a79967ca9d87fc1c77f8f472b", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": [{"url_token": "jiuyanshe", "headline": "专栏“酒研社”作者|公众号 jiuyanshe|解读每一杯酒背后的故事", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "314703062", "reply_comment_id": "314592232", "reply_root_comment_id": "314592232", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "<p>心疼，这可是高度烈酒啊，虽然有美死了的外表……</p>", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "醉酒的社长", "author_id": "ae69934d7cbd67f46b24b68289ddecba", "author_is_anonymous": false}]}, {"url_token": "ss-vero", "headline": "旅游硕士，文化遗产创新研究", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "314425955", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "314425955", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "<p>哇居然有人介绍这个了，棒。不过其实Limoncello，额，只有一个受保护的“国宝级”标签，算是正宗品（？），是索伦托的，limon di sorrento 制作的任何相关产品其实大家都有另外付这笔保护非物质文化遗产的费用。阿马尔菲的柠檬园很多，但是能进入这一标签的也是非常有限的。柠檬不同，水不同，配比不同，制作出的酒都非常不一样，远不是酸甜能讲清楚哒。在那边断断续续住了那么多次，也没做过和朋友酒厂里一样高品质的。</p><p>另外呢，limoncello其实有一个很适合大众的口味，因为正宗的味道比较强烈，加了奶油的版本（白色）入口更顺滑，菇凉们都可以喝好多。还有蜜瓜的meloncello也强烈推荐，好喝。欢迎大家过sorrento 啊。</p>", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "ss vero", "author_id": "1b2b1ba9f1d9abd104b2f91483bd3df9", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": [{"url_token": "ss-vero", "headline": "旅游硕士，文化遗产创新研究", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "317440858", "reply_comment_id": "317418491", "reply_root_comment_id": "314425955", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "<p>多练练 lol </p>", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "ss vero", "author_id": "1b2b1ba9f1d9abd104b2f91483bd3df9", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "ss-vero", "headline": "旅游硕士，文化遗产创新研究", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "317440488", "reply_comment_id": "317418491", "reply_root_comment_id": "314425955", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "<p>多练练 lol..</p>", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "ss vero", "author_id": "1b2b1ba9f1d9abd104b2f91483bd3df9", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "jiuyanshe", "headline": "专栏“酒研社”作者|公众号 jiuyanshe|解读每一杯酒背后的故事", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "317418491", "reply_comment_id": "317404172", "reply_root_comment_id": "314425955", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "<p>就怕玩脱了……都喝挂了就搞笑了……</p>", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "醉酒的社长", "author_id": "ae69934d7cbd67f46b24b68289ddecba", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "ss-vero", "headline": "旅游硕士，文化遗产创新研究", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "317404172", "reply_comment_id": "317400834", "reply_root_comment_id": "314425955", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": fal