id": "317003117", "reply_root_comment_id": "314425955", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "<p>用心理暗示告诉自己，加了奶油就不会醉不会醉~你可以试试，相信信仰的力量！（正经脸）</p>", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "醉酒的社长", "author_id": "ae69934d7cbd67f46b24b68289ddecba", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "ss-vero", "headline": "旅游硕士，文化遗产创新研究", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "317003117", "reply_comment_id": "316384655", "reply_root_comment_id": "314425955", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "<p>啊度数低一点一般。不过心理作用有大半。。</p>", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "ss vero", "author_id": "1b2b1ba9f1d9abd104b2f91483bd3df9", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "jiuyanshe", "headline": "专栏“酒研社”作者|公众号 jiuyanshe|解读每一杯酒背后的故事", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "316384655", "reply_comment_id": "316336250", "reply_root_comment_id": "314425955", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "<p>可是度数还在那里……加奶油只能醉的更甜蜜一点吧</p><p></p>", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "醉酒的社长", "author_id": "ae69934d7cbd67f46b24b68289ddecba", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "ss-vero", "headline": "旅游硕士，文化遗产创新研究", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "316336250", "reply_comment_id": "316045664", "reply_root_comment_id": "314425955", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "<p>可能是不太能喝。。所以才推荐加奶油的版本。。</p>", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "ss vero", "author_id": "1b2b1ba9f1d9abd104b2f91483bd3df9", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "jiuyanshe", "headline": "专栏“酒研社”作者|公众号 jiuyanshe|解读每一杯酒背后的故事", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "316045664", "reply_comment_id": "315626468", "reply_root_comment_id": "314425955", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "<p>传说中的自作自醉吗~</p>", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "醉酒的社长", "author_id": "ae69934d7cbd67f46b24b68289ddecba", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "ss-vero", "headline": "旅游硕士，文化遗产创新研究", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "315626468", "reply_comment_id": "314466376", "reply_root_comment_id": "314425955", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "<p>ahahah 自己做得很容易喝醉啊。。</p>", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "ss vero", "author_id": "1b2b1ba9f1d9abd104b2f91483bd3df9", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "jiuyanshe", "headline": "专栏“酒研社”作者|公众号 jiuyanshe|解读每一杯酒背后的故事", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "314466376", "reply_comment_id": "314425955", "reply_root_comment_id": "314425955", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "<p>棒~~确实自己酿造肯定会差一点，不过去不了意大利自己在家解解馋也是极好的~</p>", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "醉酒的社长", "author_id": "ae69934d7cbd67f46b24b68289ddecba", "author_is_anonymous": false}]}, {"url_token": "chen-xiao-qi-64", "headline": "霍格沃兹格兰芬多学院优秀毕业生，每天总要消失一会去拯救世界", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "314384411", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "314384411", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "<p>比列呢</p>", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "刘昴星", "author_id": "5336b0dac5c9e3104a5c9c27b90c21c6", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": [{"url_token": "jiuyanshe", "headline": "专栏“酒研社”作者|公众号 jiuyanshe|解读每一杯酒背后的故事", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "314469110", "reply_comment_id": "314384411", "reply_root_comment_id": "314384411", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "<p>大部分的用量是，柠檬三个，伏特加400ml，糖375g，水250ml，你也可以依据酿造的多少自己调配~</p>", "like_count": 1, "author_name": "醉酒的社长", "author_id": "ae69934d7cbd67f46b24b68289ddecba", "author_is_anonymous": false}]}, {"url_token": "kuang-kuang-de-mao", "headline": "淘宝", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "314370397", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "314370397", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "<p>真的要加伏特加吗？度数太高了，可以换成其他的吗？</p>", "like_count": 2, "author_name": "匡匡的猫", "author_id": "462894410a0528f7f96e964fffd94a4